nl.kb.xml.transformassert

Class TransformAssertWithTransformer

  • java.lang.Object
    • nl.kb.xml.transformassert.TransformAssertWithTransformer

  • public class TransformAssertWithTransformer
extends Object
    An instance of this class is returned by TransformAssert.describe(File)

    It exposes methods to either:

    • Declare the XML file to be transformed by the XSLT declared there:
      • whenTransforming(File, String...)
      • whenTransforming(String, String...)
    • Compare the output of the XSLT declared in there to the output of another XSLT:
      • whenComparingTo(File)
      • whenComparingTo(String)
